The burial ceremony of Hannah Atsianzale Mudavadi, the mother of ANC party leader Musalia Mudavadi, is currently underway in Mululu, Vihiga County.
President Uhuru Kenyatta arrived for the burial at around 11.30am. 
Several political leaders are in attendance including ODM leader Raila Odinga, Senate Speaker Ken Lusaka and Baringo Senator Gideon Moi.



